</span></h4>
<div>
<p>Welcome! We are now using <a href="https://byui-csm.symplicity.com/">Career Navigator</a> for all BYU-Idaho career-related postings and job seraches.</p>
<p>You'll find it's easy to register and navigate, the database has many features for your career-related needs.</p>
<h4><strong>Students and Graduates:</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>Create a profile, upload a resume and other career documents</li>
<li>Search for employers and positions by interest, location, or job discription</li>
<li>Apply for jobs and submit documents online</li>
</ul>
<h4><strong>Employers</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>Create a profile and take the opportunity to tell students about your organization, mission, etc.</li>
<li>Post jobs and have students apply online</li>
<li>Review resumes, schedules interviews and more!</li>
</ul>
<p>We appreciate your interest in careers and career services for Teacher Education students.</p>
<p>Click <a href="https://byui-csm.symplicity.com/">here</a> to get started now!</p>
